description:
Kujira no Hara tells the story of a child who is swallowed by a giant whale and discovers inside its belly a small, absurd, and wonderful world populated by a multitude of wacky characters. 

Throughout the game, 

• you will regularly obtains new weapons, allowing you to access new areas of the whale;

• you will face the hordes of bizarre monsters teeming within the whale;

• you will explore 7 large, mysterious dungeons filled with challenging puzzles;

• you will meet over 60 colorful characters also trapped inside the whale with you;

• you can help the whale's inhabitants in over 100 optional quests.

Will you manage to escape the whale?

The game's highlights are its quirky characters and its puzzle-filled dungeons. The puzzles are more difficult than in a typical Zelda game, much to the delight of puzzle enthusiasts!

The game is about 50 hours long.

It is inspired by The Legend of Zelda: The Minish Cap and Link's Awakening.
